# This directory stores trained model weights.
# The model file (dr_efficientnet_b3.keras) is too large for Git.
#
# To get the model:
#   1. Train on Google Colab using training/train.py
#   2. Download the .keras file and place it here
#   3. The backend will automatically detect and load it
#
# Without the model file, the backend runs in MOCK mode
# with simulated predictions.
